17:21.874 --> 17:23.376
(thunder rumbles)

17:23.410 --> 17:25.412
(panting)

17:37.757 --> 17:39.726
(heartbeat pulsing)

17:39.759 --> 17:41.761
(woman panting)

17:44.464 --> 17:46.466
("Varú " resumes playing)

