(whispering):
It's okay.

19:29.035 --> 19:30.670
It's okay.

19:31.704 --> 19:33.706
It's okay.

19:37.710 --> 19:39.712
(choir singing)

19:47.787 --> 19:50.723
(whispering):
Oh, my God.

19:53.526 --> 19:56.095
I get it.

19:59.566 --> 20:01.568
I get it.

